       Welcome to OSF/MotifTM, a user environment based on the X
       Window System designed to make your interaction with your
       computer easier and more productive.

       This guide is intended to teach you the fundamentals of
       working with MotifTM.  More specifically, you will learn how
       to:

          +o Create and manipulate windows on your screen

          +o Use application programs written for the Motif environ-
            ment

          +o Personalize your Motif environment to suit your own
            needs and tastes





























